==English==
=== Noun ===
'''maturity'''
# The state of being ready or [[ripe]]
# When bodily growth has completed and [[reproduction]] can begin
#* The entire tank of [[:w:guppy|guppies]] was in their '''maturity''' and ready to mate.
# In [[finance]], ready for [[execution]] or coming due
#* The note was cashed at '''maturity'''.

